name: Calgary Taekwondo Academy
overview: For parents who are looking to enroll their children in a physical activity program that builds focus, self-discipline, and increase self-discipline and concentration, Calgary Taekwondo Academy provides a and specialized Taekwondo program that combines education and physical training in a structured program that brings youth together in a friendly, safe and competitive environment. Calgary Taekwondo Academy is Calgary based company that has a focus on being the leader in Taekwondo for the Calgary Region. Unlike other Martial Arts studios that may offer Taekwondo as an option, Calgary Taekwondo not only specializes in Taekwondo, has the dedicated facilities to properly train people of all ages.
